{
  "name": "RPlog_Tidepool_Adventure",
  "title": "Tidepool Adventure",
  "summary": "Seizing a rare moment unwatched while her Jedi guardian Leo is away, the ambassador's daughter Gabi slips down a cliff to the tide pools of a windswept beach to play and forage. Picking her barefoot way across the ancient reef, she washes in the seawater, hunts among the pools, and pierces her finger on a venomous sea urchin -- exactly the prize she sought. Improvising tools from driftwood and seaweed, she carefully pries the urchin loose and, guilty at the thought of killing it, snaps off just a handful of envenomated spines before returning it to the water. Back in their cave hideaway before Leo's return, she weaves the spines into a crude spear-tip and, curling up to nap, plays the holo-recording of her mother's voice -- a lullaby and a message urging her to sort lies from truth, fear nothing, and obey the Jedi until her mother can return -- and drifts into sleep.",
